Background

The contributors to the CP method come from diverse backgrounds including being directly or indirectly involved in the design, development, deployment, and scaling of applications from Startups to the Fortune 500; leading Machine Learning Research Teams; and leading high performance Navy SEAL teams into combat.

We seek to pioneer and promote better ways of developing software by leveraging technology and automation to push the bounds of Agile Software Development.We are advocating for organizations to adopt Continuous Previews as an Agile-supporting method to improve and expedite how they build and test software. 
